features: Fireproof and water-resistant safe: Fireproof file storage bag is made of double layered non-itchy silicone coated fiberglass which stands up the temperature up to 2000℉.It has been passed by SGS TEST(UL94 VTM-0 Certified).Fireproof bag is not only fireproof but also high water resistant in case it gets wet for any reason.Nothing is completely foolproof, but added protection is always a good idea.

Large capacity: 14.2*10.6*4 inches large fireproof file bag has three-layer of design.This includes 8 passport mesh bags, 16 card slots, 4 U Disk pockets, 7 folder layers and one main pocket with a large space. It can store your important documents,files,money,passport,U Disk,cards,laptop,certificates in a safe and orderly way.Great way to organize your files easy for you to find whatever files you looking for quickly.

Multiple security protection: Design with a strong grab handle for carrying everything you needed easily,2 way water resistant zippers make it easier to open and close the bag,combination locks are designed to make your valuables safer,and more wider strap handle design on the back allows you to insert a suitcase handle.(with instructions for using the lock)

Easier to store: If you are worried that your valuable documents will be damaged by fire,or your papers are cluttered, it will be a good helper to protect your valuable documents. Not only can you put it in your home, office, car, safe box, storage cabinet, you can also take it to camping, travel and various outdoor activities. Of course, also it will be a great Christmas gift for dad.

Trusted after sales service:How can we better protect our valuables from any fire? DocSafe keep researching and developing on fireproof materials,safety technology.We only wish to present the best to customers,to protect your valuables.If there any quality problem, please feel free to let us know.We promise to arrange a replacement or 100% refund immediately. Ready to respond within a 24 hour time,your suggestion has a great impact on the upgrade of our products.

To set your personal combination, follow these steps: Need to snap the zipper into the lock hole. 1.Put the dials at original number 0-0-0. 2.Press down the reset button (a)with a tool until hear the "Click" sound. 3.Set your combination by turning the dials(b),for example 8-8-8. 4.Push the button(c) towards to the direction of arrow and the reset button(a) will be back when you hear the "Click" sound. Now you have finished to set your personal combination.Please remember your personal combination by heart. You can repeat the above steps if you want to reset your password

Three layer design Our original Intention: Accidents happen when we least expect, and there’s nothing more devastating than a fire that takes away valuable paperwork, personal information, pictures or achievements.That’s why we developed the fireproof document bag- Protect your financials, personal information,document notebook, that won’t let you down when emergency strikes. Nothing is completely foolproof, but added protection is always a good idea.Fireproof does not mean it could support endless fire exposure, please keep any fire exposure to the minimum.Do not immerse or wash the bag in liquid.If you have any questions about the use of the combination lock, please check the manual.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Solid, lightweight document bag with nice organization features
reviews.reviewText: I am quite impressed, for the price, about the size and quality of the bag. It seems sturdy enough to handle any wear and tear, and really has some nice organizational features. No idea if it will withstand a fire or water dousing, but it seems like very good value for what it offers. I highly recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Security box for important papers is great!
reviews.reviewText: Very roomy and lots of space for folders, paperwork and important things like passports, credit cards. Soft and can be compressed a bit to fit in a tight spot.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Outer cover sticky
reviews.reviewText: I like everything about this except the sticky feeling on the outer shell.The sleeves where a bit disappointing, because you can’t slide a standard piece of paper in unless folded. There’s plenty of room for folders/paperwork in the open compartment. I wished the shell was a bit sturdier, but I guess it wouldn’t be considered flame retardant if there was plastic or pressed cardboard inserts.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Works well, many pockets/pouches, lock not easy to use

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Loved the product. Seems to be of good quality even the chain looks like can hold the water. This is perfect to lock your documents in case if you are going somewhere else or can also be your small carry case for a business trip

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars not hard walled
reviews.reviewText: the images made it seem like a case with hard walls, similar to first aid kits. they are definitely not. everything else is cool though.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great portable safe bag
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for a place to keep all our documents and other items organized all in one easy place that I could grab and go. We have had a lot of leaks from the roof in my apartment over the years and I wanted to make sure our items were safe and secure. Easy to carry and in one place so I didn't have to go searching all over for everyone's documents and this was what I needed.I love the different compartments so that things can be organized as well. And the accordion folder fit into very nicely as well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good for important documents
reviews.reviewText: The built-in lock is great to help everything stay safe. The pockets for ID’s and passports are also very useful.
Great price. Perfect size use it to transfer a few file folders from home office to shop.

reviews.reviewerName: Have a nice day :)Have a nice day :)
reviews.reviewText: The bag is very versatile and can fit tons of documents. A full 2" 3 ring binder can fit easily. Has a few pouches to keep loose items like CD Rom (yes I keep them there) ans USB sticks. There is a 3 digit lock so it is safe. The texture and material is well made and easy to clean. Seems to be water proof from spills.
Looks slightly smaller and different from the picture uploaded by seller
The product is useful for document storage.
